4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners. Over 16 weeks, students engage in three classes per week with a maximum of 12 participants. The course covers key skills such as Python, SQL, Looker, and statistics, enabling students to create predictive models and work with both supervised and unsupervised learning algorithms. Participants will also strategize and develop their AI projects, ensuring privacy and security throughout the lifecycle. No prior experience is required, and instruction is available in English and Spanish. Graduates receive recognized certificates. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop